name: H3CClientX
body:
### Introduction
H3CClientX is an H3C-specialized 802.1x protocol authentication client including a front-end monitor, based on previous work [h3cclient b1](http://sourceforge.net/projects/h3cclient/) by asklux. This client has been verified working for students from Shandong University.

### Downloads
##### v0.9.0 Pre-release: [Download Installer](https://dl.dropbox.com/s/gjrka8a7q4kmd9n/H3CClient.0.9.0.zip)
* Feature: Basic functionality of interacting with authentication server.
* Feature: Checking for further updates.

### Contact & Support
If any bugs encountered or support needed, please submit a bug report via [Github Issues](https://github.com/5Ki3s0x1C9/OS-X-H3CClient/issues). 
Reverse engineering of the H3C protocol credits to the efforts of previous work.
